Start Point: Talk to the Priest of Trinimac, in the Falkreath Graveyard

Official Difficulty: Experienced

Description: An Altmer warrior, follower of Trinimac, wishes to create a bow-sword, a combination of archery and sword-fighting. Will you help him?

Official length: Short

Requirements: None

Items required: Daedric Bow, Daedric Sword

Enemies to defeat: None

Quest Stages: 

Rewards: None
